1
00:00:22,689 --> 00:00:26,026
<i>Kau tahu kenapa aku memilih mereka?</i>

2
00:00:29,946 --> 00:00:33,783
<i>Kenapa aku memilih mereka
untuk membentuk semula dunia ini?</i>

3
00:00:34,617 --> 00:00:37,954
Sebab mereka lemah.

4
00:00:39,456 --> 00:00:41,916
<i>Mudah dipatahkan.</i>

5
00:00:44,961 --> 00:00:46,963
<i>Mudah dibentuk semula.</i>

6
00:00:47,589 --> 00:00:49,049
<i>Mudah dikawal.</i>

7
00:00:51,217 --> 00:00:53,803
<i>Wadah yang sempurna.</i>

8
00:00:57,891 --> 00:00:59,058
Sayang.

9
00:00:59,059 --> 00:01:00,976
- Mak.
- Aduhai, sayang.

10
00:01:00,977 --> 00:01:03,771
Mak tak faham. Macam mana kamu...

11
00:01:03,772 --> 00:01:04,897
Dia ahli sihir.

12
00:01:04,898 --> 00:01:07,107
Ahli sihir sebenar.

13
00:01:07,108 --> 00:01:08,234
Mike.

14
00:01:10,361 --> 00:01:11,403
Kau berjaya.

15
00:01:11,404 --> 00:01:12,781
Kau berjaya buat.

16
00:01:15,617 --> 00:01:16,533
Budak-budak itu.

17
00:01:16,534 --> 00:01:18,786
Vecna dapat tangkap budak-budak itu.

18
00:01:18,787 --> 00:01:21,081
Aku tahu. Derek, Mary, Glenn.

19
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:24,417
Tak. Bukan mereka saja.

20
00:01:26,544 --> 00:01:29,380
<i>Yang lain pun
tak sempat keluar dari Hawkins.</i>

21
00:01:31,049 --> 00:01:34,594
<i>Aku boleh tolong lawan
kalau aku bertindak lebih awal.</i>

22
00:01:36,346 --> 00:01:37,388
<i>Tapi aku lambat.</i>

23
00:01:38,765 --> 00:01:40,725
<i>Sekarang dia dah tangkap mereka.</i>

24
00:01:42,143 --> 00:01:43,394
<i>Kesemua 12.</i>

25
00:01:45,980 --> 00:01:47,107
Kita gagal.

26
00:01:48,650 --> 00:01:49,566
Saya gagal.

27
00:01:49,567 --> 00:01:50,485
Tidak.

28
00:01:56,199 --> 00:01:57,951
Terowong. Radio Shack.

29
00:02:47,041 --> 00:02:51,337
<i>Mungkin kamu tak ingat sangat
macam mana kamu boleh ada di sini.</i>

30
00:02:52,338 --> 00:02:53,338
- Mary!
<i>- Keliru.</i>

31
00:02:53,339 --> 00:02:54,339
Holly!

32
00:02:54,340 --> 00:02:56,967
<i>Raksasa-raksasa itu cuba tangkap kamu.</i>

33
00:02:56,968 --> 00:02:57,927
Hai!

34
00:02:58,511 --> 00:03:00,304
<i>Tapi saya sempat selamatkan.</i>

35
00:03:00,305 --> 00:03:01,763
- Apa khabar?
- Baik.

36
00:03:01,764 --> 00:03:02,849
<i>Tempat ini,</i>

37
00:03:03,474 --> 00:03:04,475
<i>rumah saya,</i>

38
00:03:05,101 --> 00:03:06,603
<i>rumah kamu juga sekarang.</i>

39
00:03:07,187 --> 00:03:08,354
<i>Tempat berlindung.</i>

40
00:03:08,938 --> 00:03:11,773
<i>Asalkan tak pergi
ke hutan yang dipenuhi raksasa,</i>

41
00:03:11,774 --> 00:03:13,483
<i>kamu selamat di sini.</i>

42
00:03:13,484 --> 00:03:16,570
<i>Saya tahu ramai antara kamu
yang tertanya-tanya,</i>

43
00:03:16,571 --> 00:03:19,574
<i>bila kawan-kawan
dan keluarga kamu akan datang?</i>

44
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:24,245
Tapi banyak lagi dalam taruhan
selain nyawa insan yang kamu sayang.

45
00:03:26,289 --> 00:03:27,999
Saya tak nak buat kamu takut.

46
00:03:28,833 --> 00:03:31,502
Tapi kamu cukup berani
untuk tahu hal sebenar.

47
00:03:32,086 --> 00:03:35,631
Kegelapan jahat sedang merebak
bukan saja di Hawkins,

48
00:03:35,632 --> 00:03:36,924
malah seluruh dunia.

49
00:03:36,925 --> 00:03:40,011
Tak lama lagi, ia takkan dapat dihentikan.

50
00:03:40,637 --> 00:03:44,848
Anggaplah kegelapan ini
macam Black Thing dalam buku kamu.

51
00:03:44,849 --> 00:03:49,269
Kegelapan ini ugut keluarga kamu
macam Black Thing ugut keluarga Meg, tapi,

52
00:03:49,270 --> 00:03:52,189
saya dah jumpa cara
untuk tewaskan kegelapan ini.

53
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:53,483
Macam mana?

54
00:03:55,109 --> 00:03:59,530
Saya mengembara jauh
ke luar dimensi kita buat masa yang lama.

55
00:04:00,114 --> 00:04:02,742
Dalam kembara itu,
saya menemukan dunia lain.

56
00:04:03,701 --> 00:04:05,244
Dunia yang jauh dari Bumi.

57
00:04:05,245 --> 00:04:08,706
Dunia itu serupa dengan dunia kita, tapi,

58
00:04:09,582 --> 00:04:10,708
semuanya baik-baik.

59
00:04:11,459 --> 00:04:13,294
Tak ada raksasa dan kegelapan.

60
00:04:14,712 --> 00:04:15,838
Hanya ada cahaya.

61
00:04:16,422 --> 00:04:19,342
Inilah sebab sebenar kamu semua dipilih.

62
00:04:19,842 --> 00:04:20,760
Kamu...

63
00:04:21,511 --> 00:04:23,263
tak seperti budak-budak lain.

64
00:04:23,846 --> 00:04:26,057
Macam Meg juga, kamu istimewa.

65
00:04:27,058 --> 00:04:29,060
Kamu ada kuasa terpendam di sini.

66
00:04:30,228 --> 00:04:33,939
Sekiranya kita bekerjasama,
kita boleh membangkitkan kuasa itu,

67
00:04:33,940 --> 00:04:37,192
menyalurkan tenaga kita
dan menarik dunia baharu itu.

68
00:04:37,193 --> 00:04:38,903
Apabila cahaya itu

69
00:04:40,405 --> 00:04:41,781
mendatangi kegelapan,

70
00:04:42,365 --> 00:04:44,117
kegelapan akan terhapus,

71
00:04:44,701 --> 00:04:47,120
insan tersayang akan selamat, dan kamu...

72
00:04:49,289 --> 00:04:50,623
Kamu akan jadi wira.

73
00:04:55,378 --> 00:04:56,963
Ya, Holly?

74
00:04:57,755 --> 00:05:00,091
Awak akan keluar lagi?

75
00:05:01,009 --> 00:05:03,593
Untuk bawa budak istimewa lain ke sini?

76
00:05:03,594 --> 00:05:05,972
Kasihan Holly. Dia pertama dipilih.

77
00:05:06,889 --> 00:05:08,849
Dia ditinggalkan seorang diri.

78
00:05:08,850 --> 00:05:11,644
Tapi jangan risau.
Saya takkan tinggalkan kamu.

79
00:05:12,395 --> 00:05:14,062
Tinggalkan sesiapa pun lagi.

80
00:05:14,063 --> 00:05:15,648
Tapi buat masa sekarang,

81
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:18,484
makan dan main puas-puas.

82
00:05:19,610 --> 00:05:21,362
Paling penting, berehat.

83
00:05:22,405 --> 00:05:23,489
Sebab esok?

84
00:05:25,783 --> 00:05:27,160
Esok, ia akan bermula.

85
00:06:31,641 --> 00:06:38,648
BABAK LIMA: OPERASI KEJUTAN

86
00:07:01,379 --> 00:07:02,879
Kata tak ada yang keluar?

87
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:04,965
Unit Keselamatan sendiri kata.

88
00:07:04,966 --> 00:07:06,842
Mereka lesap macam Houdini?

89
00:07:06,843 --> 00:07:07,968
Saya tak tahu, tuan.

90
00:07:07,969 --> 00:07:10,053
Periksa setiap ceruk bangunan ini.

91
00:07:10,054 --> 00:07:14,225
Setiap bilik, lubang dan panel akses.
Mari pergi. Gerak. Gerak!

92
00:07:51,971 --> 00:07:52,971
Awak okey tak?

93
00:07:52,972 --> 00:07:55,224
Ia dah hilang.

94
00:07:56,184 --> 00:07:57,476
Kita terlalu jauh.

95
00:07:57,477 --> 00:08:00,854
Tak apa. Kita dah cukup jauh.
Mereka takkan dapat kejar.

96
00:08:00,855 --> 00:08:02,482
Hebat betul helah kamu.

97
00:08:03,608 --> 00:08:06,402
Sekejap, mungkin saya patut kata "gempak".

98
00:08:07,153 --> 00:08:09,655
Kamu yang ajar El perkataan itu, bukan?

99
00:08:10,239 --> 00:08:13,366
Saya bawa pengaruh tak baik.

100
00:08:13,367 --> 00:08:15,703
Ya, samalah kita.

101
00:08:30,927 --> 00:08:32,677
- Lucas?
- Aduhai.

102
00:08:32,678 --> 00:08:34,513
- Tidak.
- Hei, semua.

103
00:08:34,514 --> 00:08:35,598
Tidak.

104
00:08:36,849 --> 00:08:37,682
Alamak.

105
00:08:37,683 --> 00:08:39,059
Calar sikit saja.

106
00:08:39,060 --> 00:08:41,394
- Alat pertolongan cemas.
- Alamak!

107
00:08:41,395 --> 00:08:43,104
Sekejap.

108
00:08:43,105 --> 00:08:44,899
- Boleh angkat? Tunjuk.
- Ya.

109
00:08:48,110 --> 00:08:49,819
Taklah teruk sangat.

110
00:08:49,820 --> 00:08:50,946
Aduh.

111
00:08:50,947 --> 00:08:55,158
Ya, baru nampak ganas nanti
kalau ada parut macam itu.

112
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:57,369
Maaf sebab gagal melindungi mereka.

113
00:08:57,370 --> 00:09:01,289
Kau dah cuba sedaya upaya.
Kau lawan. Kau bahayakan nyawa kau.

114
00:09:01,290 --> 00:09:02,416
Padu ayunan kau.

115
00:09:04,293 --> 00:09:05,294
Kau nampak?

116
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,213
Bukan setakat nampak.

117
00:09:09,298 --> 00:09:14,302
Jadi, Demo terapung,
tangan dan kaki patah, kemudian mati.

118
00:09:14,303 --> 00:09:16,388
Itu semua kerja kau?

119
00:09:16,389 --> 00:09:19,140
Ya, begitulah.

120
00:09:19,141 --> 00:09:20,309
Gilalah.

121
00:09:21,727 --> 00:09:22,853
Gilalah.

122
00:09:23,437 --> 00:09:27,941
Kau tahu apa maknanya, bukan?
Kau betul-betul macam Will Yang Bijaksana.

123
00:09:27,942 --> 00:09:30,777
- Tak juga.
- Dia ahli sihir, bukan ahli jampi.

124
00:09:30,778 --> 00:09:33,196
Okey. Ya, mungkinlah.

125
00:09:33,197 --> 00:09:35,240
Tapi kau faham maksud aku, bukan?

126
00:09:35,241 --> 00:09:37,701
Ini betul-betul mengubah keadaan.

127
00:09:37,702 --> 00:09:39,119
Kita ada El kedua.

128
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:41,997
Aku bukan El kedua. Aku tak ada kuasa.

129
00:09:41,998 --> 00:09:44,916
Aku cuma menyedut, mencuri kuasa Vecna.

130
00:09:44,917 --> 00:09:47,460
Aku perlu dekat dengan minda sarang.

131
00:09:47,461 --> 00:09:48,878
Vecna takkan kembali.

132
00:09:48,879 --> 00:09:51,047
- Tapi Demo mungkin kembali.
- Tak.

133
00:09:51,048 --> 00:09:53,258
Mereka dah dapat budak-budak itu,

134
00:09:53,259 --> 00:09:55,177
jadi dia dah ada wadahnya.

135
00:09:59,724 --> 00:10:00,724
"Wadah"?

136
00:10:00,725 --> 00:10:03,143
Dia panggil mereka wadah.

137
00:10:03,144 --> 00:10:06,146
Dia cakap,
"Wadah untuk membentuk semula dunia."

138
00:10:06,147 --> 00:10:08,190
Aku cuma harap teori kau salah.

139
00:10:09,108 --> 00:10:10,026
Teori apa?

140
00:10:10,943 --> 00:10:12,069
6 November.

141
00:10:13,321 --> 00:10:14,989
Hari semua ini bermula

142
00:10:16,490 --> 00:10:17,742
ialah hari ia berakhir.

143
00:10:22,538 --> 00:10:23,372
Kau okey?

144
00:10:28,753 --> 00:10:31,464
{\an8}Okey, Lucas. Perlahan-lahan.

145
00:10:31,964 --> 00:10:33,466
{\an8}Pegang tangan aku.

146
00:10:35,134 --> 00:10:36,801
Tahan sikit. Selangkah lagi.

147
00:10:36,802 --> 00:10:38,971
Hei. Mari sini.

148
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:44,893
Ada cara tak untuk berhubung
dengan minda sarang sekali lagi

149
00:10:44,894 --> 00:10:46,603
dan akses kuasa dia semula?

150
00:10:46,604 --> 00:10:48,438
Mustahil, melainkan...

151
00:10:48,439 --> 00:10:50,483
Sarang itu dekat. Mak tahu.

152
00:10:51,192 --> 00:10:54,736
Tapi kejadian tadi pun
kita sangka mustahil sebelum ini.

153
00:10:54,737 --> 00:10:55,821
Mak.

154
00:10:56,364 --> 00:10:57,989
Maksud mak, mungkin...

155
00:10:57,990 --> 00:11:00,200
Mungkin kali ini,

156
00:11:00,201 --> 00:11:02,827
jangan guna kuasa untuk lawan tentera dia.

157
00:11:02,828 --> 00:11:04,621
Guna kuasa untuk lawan dia.

158
00:11:04,622 --> 00:11:06,498
Lawan Vecna.

159
00:11:06,499 --> 00:11:08,667
Tikam dia dengan pedangnya sendiri.

160
00:11:08,668 --> 00:11:10,878
Kamu tak gagal malam ini.

161
00:11:11,921 --> 00:11:13,214
Apa yang kamu buat

162
00:11:14,131 --> 00:11:16,133
betul-betul luar biasa.

163
00:11:16,967 --> 00:11:18,760
Kamu sendiri yang cakap.

164
00:11:18,761 --> 00:11:22,431
Vecna pilih kamu
sebab dia pandang rendah kamu.

165
00:11:23,057 --> 00:11:25,475
Kami semua pandang rendah. Lagi-lagi mak.

166
00:11:25,476 --> 00:11:29,563
Itu satu kesilapan
yang mak takkan sekali-kali buat lagi.

167
00:11:30,231 --> 00:11:33,650
Tapi mak berani bertaruh
yang dia akan buat silap itu lagi.

168
00:11:33,651 --> 00:11:35,318
Apabila ia berlaku,

169
00:11:35,319 --> 00:11:39,573
itulah kesilapan terakhir
yang anak haram itu akan buat.

170
00:11:53,462 --> 00:11:56,132
Ajaib betul mereka kembali dengan selamat.

171
00:11:57,049 --> 00:12:01,470
Malangnya Bimmer mahal Harrington
tak dapat diselamatkan.

172
00:12:02,805 --> 00:12:04,557
Awak nak buat macam ini?

173
00:12:05,057 --> 00:12:07,309
Buat lawak macam tak ada apa-apa jadi?

174
00:12:11,856 --> 00:12:14,315
Rancangannya, awak cari Vecna dan balik.

175
00:12:14,316 --> 00:12:16,443
- Tapi awak ada rancangan lain.
- Taklah.

176
00:12:16,444 --> 00:12:17,694
Tipu.

177
00:12:17,695 --> 00:12:19,612
Macam pasal masa latihan saya.

178
00:12:19,613 --> 00:12:23,658
Awak tak nak saya ikut menyusup
sebab awak nak bunuh Vecna dan mati.

179
00:12:23,659 --> 00:12:27,370
Hei, dengar sini.
Kejadian hari ini berbeza.

180
00:12:27,371 --> 00:12:30,957
Kamu tak mampu lawan Kryptonite.
Saya tak ada pilihan lain.

181
00:12:30,958 --> 00:12:32,001
Bom itu pula?

182
00:12:32,668 --> 00:12:35,503
Bom itu cuma langkah berjaga-jaga.

183
00:12:35,504 --> 00:12:38,340
Langkah berjaga-jaga
yang orang lain tak tahu.

184
00:12:40,217 --> 00:12:42,136
Saya nampak mata awak tadi.

185
00:12:43,679 --> 00:12:44,805
Saya nampak.

186
00:12:46,223 --> 00:12:48,100
Awak memang rancang nak mati.

187
00:12:51,187 --> 00:12:52,646
Sejak awal lagi.

188
00:12:55,733 --> 00:12:56,734
Hei!

189
00:12:57,359 --> 00:12:59,820
Kawan awak sepatutnya di sini, bukan?

190
00:13:12,166 --> 00:13:13,834
Aduhai, tolonglah.

191
00:13:31,936 --> 00:13:33,686
Cerah harapan kita nampaknya.

192
00:13:33,687 --> 00:13:34,939
Kita di lobi.

193
00:13:35,564 --> 00:13:39,317
Sebenarnya, kita nak ke mana?

194
00:13:39,318 --> 00:13:42,779
Itulah. Apa benda yang kita cari?

195
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:44,447
Tengok <i>Return of the Jedi?</i>

196
00:13:44,448 --> 00:13:46,241
- Ada beruang teddy?
- Ewok.

197
00:13:46,242 --> 00:13:47,534
Terbaik dalam francais.

198
00:13:47,535 --> 00:13:48,451
- Yakah?
- Ya?

199
00:13:48,452 --> 00:13:51,162
Tak, tapi semua budak suka. Tak hairanlah.

200
00:13:51,163 --> 00:13:54,874
Dalam filem itu, pemberontak perlu
musnahkan Death Star kedua,

201
00:13:54,875 --> 00:13:59,045
tapi ada perisai tenaga pelindung
yang dicipta oleh penjana perisai.

202
00:13:59,046 --> 00:14:02,298
Susah-susah saja jelaskan filem
yang kami dah tengok.

203
00:14:02,299 --> 00:14:04,468
Yang peliknya, filem itu relevan.

204
00:14:05,052 --> 00:14:09,514
Aku rasa tembok daging bulat ini
sebenarnya perisai tenaga versi Vecna,

205
00:14:09,515 --> 00:14:11,266
cuma ia bukan fiksyen sains.

206
00:14:11,267 --> 00:14:15,353
Ini kuasa ghaib
yang dicipta oleh sihir gelap Vecna.

207
00:14:15,354 --> 00:14:19,566
Perisai sihir ini yang halang kita masuk
dan selamatkan Holly.

208
00:14:19,567 --> 00:14:23,027
Kalau betul kiraan aku,
penjananya ada di makmal ini.

209
00:14:23,028 --> 00:14:26,406
Jadi, kalau kita jumpa
penjana perisai sihir gelap itu...

210
00:14:26,407 --> 00:14:28,616
- Musnahkan tembok.
- Cari Vecna, selamatkan Holly.

211
00:14:28,617 --> 00:14:29,701
Pingat untuk semua.

212
00:14:29,702 --> 00:14:31,369
Macam mana rupa benda itu?

213
00:14:31,370 --> 00:14:33,163
Manalah aku tahu.

214
00:14:49,138 --> 00:14:50,139
Atas atau bawah?

215
00:14:51,223 --> 00:14:53,933
Dua-dua. Berpecah.
Dapat periksa banyak tempat.

216
00:14:53,934 --> 00:14:57,061
Ya, saya tak kisah,
tapi boleh kita tukar pasukan?

217
00:14:57,062 --> 00:14:58,855
Nance, kita berdua naik?

218
00:14:58,856 --> 00:15:00,481
- Saya...
- Kau seriuslah?

219
00:15:00,482 --> 00:15:02,275
Kami perlukan ruang.

220
00:15:02,276 --> 00:15:03,192
- Ya.
- Tolonglah.

221
00:15:03,193 --> 00:15:04,485
Baik. Kita berdua?

222
00:15:04,486 --> 00:15:05,904
Kita pun perlu ruang.

223
00:15:05,905 --> 00:15:08,616
Semua tak boleh kecuali Nancy.
Senang betul.

224
00:15:09,116 --> 00:15:11,367
Hei, kita tak ada masa.

225
00:15:11,368 --> 00:15:13,119
Ikut pasukan biasa saja.

226
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:14,537
- Tak boleh...
- Saya...

227
00:15:14,538 --> 00:15:15,456
Muktamad.

228
00:15:18,459 --> 00:15:19,668
Bagus.

229
00:15:22,963 --> 00:15:24,173
Bagus sangat.

