380
00:24:05,444 --> 00:24:07,153
Apa maksud awak?

381
00:24:07,154 --> 00:24:08,612
Entah. Nada suara awak.

382
00:24:08,613 --> 00:24:10,072
- Nada suara?
- Ya.

383
00:24:10,073 --> 00:24:12,908
- Okey.
- Nampak? Nada suara itulah.

384
00:24:12,909 --> 00:24:18,248
Ya, nada suara saya macam itu
sebab awak tiba-tiba merepek.

385
