Ya, di bawah tadi pun saya merepek?

386
00:24:22,544 --> 00:24:26,505
Maksud awak, waktu awak dan Steve
mula nak berlagak maco lagi?

387
00:24:26,506 --> 00:24:31,051
Tak, waktu Steve ajak awak ikut dia,
dan awak teragak-agak.

388
00:24:31,052 --> 00:24:34,598
Sebenarnya, saya cakap
kita patut ikut pasukan biasa.

389
00:24:35,223 --> 00:24:36,932
Ya, tapi awak teragak-agak.

390
00:24:36,933 --> 00:24:38,350
Saya tak teragak-agak.

391
00:24:38,351 --> 00:24:40,187
Saya kenal awak. Awak teragak-agak.

392
00:24:41,396 --> 00:24:44,398
Okey. Saya tak teragak-agak,
tapi kalau betul pun?

393
00:24:44,399 --> 00:24:46,108
Itu tak penting.

394
00:24:46,109 --> 00:24:48,110
Adik saya hilang.

395
00:24:48,111 --> 00:24:50,822
Ya, sebab itulah ia penting.

396
00:24:51,490 --> 00:24:53,866
Selepas semua benda yang dah berlaku,

397
00:24:53,867 --> 00:24:55,284
yang tengah berlaku,

398
00:24:55,285 --> 00:24:57,578
