Awak buat apa?

420
00:26:41,224 --> 00:26:42,183
Jonathan!

421
00:26:45,979 --> 00:26:47,230
Apa benda ini?

422
00:26:48,064 --> 00:26:49,608
Apa itu?

423
00:26:50,609 --> 00:26:53,862
Dah terlambatkah
untuk saya setuju dengan teori Dustin?

424
00:27:01,703 --> 00:27:04,998
<i>Nancy, Jonathan, dengar tak?</i> Over.

425
00:27:06,082 --> 00:27:10,127
Kami dah sampai di gereja.
Kami tercari-cari kamu di mana.

426
00:27:10,128 --> 00:27:11,254
Dengar tak?

427
00:27:13,173 --> 00:27:14,215
Jonathan!

428
00:27:15,258 --> 00:27:17,010
Nancy, dengar tak?

429
00:27:18,219 --> 00:27:19,428
Tolonglah.

430
00:27:19,429 --> 00:27:22,057
<i>Awak dan polis itu datang jauh-jauh.</i>

431
00:27:22,724 --> 00:27:26,477
Mesti kamu terkejut
jumpa saya di situ, bukan Henry.

432
00:27:26,478 --> 00:27:27,937
Saya minta maaf, Kali.

433
00:27:28,813 --> 00:27:31,066
Maaf sebab tak jumpa awak lebih awal.

434
00:27:31,733 --> 00:27:33,025
Awak bukannya tahu.

435
00:27:33,026 --> 00:27:36,613
Saya ada tab mandi, tangki di rumah.

436
00:27:39,032 --> 00:27:41,368
Saya boleh cari jauh. Sini pun boleh.

437
00:27:42,577 --> 00:27:46,122
Rasanya saya takut nak cari awak.

438
00:27:47,207 --> 00:27:49,500
Setakat mana awak tahu tentang Henry?

439
00:27:49,501 --> 00:27:52,337
Semuanya, kecuali...

440
00:27:54,464 --> 00:27:56,424
dia masih hidup.

441
00:27:57,842 --> 00:27:59,260
Tolong saya cari dia,

442
00:28:00,595 --> 00:28:01,428
bunuh dia.

443
00:28:01,429 --> 00:28:02,471
Kemudian apa?

444
00:28:02,472 --> 00:28:03,765
Ia akan berakhir.

445
00:28:04,265 --> 00:28:06,934
Barulah kita boleh hidup.
Betul-betul hidup.

446
00:28:06,935 --> 00:28:08,519
Itu cuma angan-angan.

447
00:28:08,520 --> 00:28:10,105
Tak semestinya.

448
00:28:11,523 --> 00:28:14,734
Dulu saya pun ada angan-angan yang sama.

449
00:28:15,443 --> 00:28:17,696
Saya mampu hentikan semuanya.

450
00:28:19,364 --> 00:28:20,490
Saya mampu

451
00:28:22,325 --> 00:28:24,327
sembuhkan luka kita.

452
00:28:31,459 --> 00:28:32,836
<i>Tapi mereka jumpa saya.</i>

453
00:28:34,170 --> 00:28:35,796
<i>Jumpa kawan-kawan saya.</i>

454
00:28:35,797 --> 00:28:36,965
Tidak!

455
00:28:37,549 --> 00:28:38,508
Bunuh mereka.

456
00:28:40,093 --> 00:28:41,469
Mereka tahan saya.

457
00:29:25,013 --> 00:29:28,098
<i>Saya tak faham
kenapa saya dibiarkan hidup.</i>

458
00:29:28,099 --> 00:29:33,104
<i>Saya ingat mungkin doktor itu ditugaskan
untuk menyeksa saya.</i>

