<i>Tak seperti darah Henry.</i>

693
00:46:18,692 --> 00:46:24,656
<i>Hakikatnya, anak-anak Papa hanyalah
hasil tiruan Henry yang tak setara.</i>

694
00:46:25,365 --> 00:46:27,034
Seorang saja daripada kita

695
00:46:28,076 --> 00:46:29,703
yang betul-betul macam dia.

696
00:46:30,454 --> 00:46:34,540
Ini cuma ilusi. Ia tak benar.
Semua ini tak benar.

697
00:46:34,541 --> 00:46:37,418
Kenapa Kay beria-ia sangat nak cari awak?

698
00:46:37,419 --> 00:46:41,590
Mereka akan cari awak
dan cipta lebih ramai orang macam awak!

699
00:46:43,050 --> 00:46:43,926
Macam Henry.

700
00:46:53,727 --> 00:46:55,521
Tak ada penamat gembira, Jane.

701
00:46:56,104 --> 00:46:57,397
Ia bukan untuk kita.

702
00:47:01,026 --> 00:47:03,278
Hei, tak apa. Ini saya.

703
00:47:04,112 --> 00:47:05,447
Ini saya.

704
00:47:30,764 --> 00:47:32,432
Barat laut.

705
00:47:33,809 --> 00:47:35,102
Sesat jalan, ya?

706
00:47:49,825 --> 00:47:51,158
Siapa beri peta ini?

707
00:47:51,159 --> 00:47:52,743
Mak kau!

708
00:47:52,744 --> 00:47:53,996
Pandang aku!

709
00:47:54,997 --> 00:47:56,790
Kalau kau tipu aku lagi,

710
00:47:57,624 --> 00:48:02,379
aku akan bunuh bapak kau yang bodoh...

711
00:48:04,715 --> 00:48:07,384
mak kau yang celaka...

712
00:48:10,304 --> 00:48:14,141
dan kakak kau yang sial.

713
00:48:18,270 --> 00:48:20,480
Baiklah, sayang. Masa main dah tamat.

714
00:48:21,732 --> 00:48:22,608
Mari masuk.

715
00:48:23,233 --> 00:48:25,318
Kenapa masam saja muka?

716
00:48:25,319 --> 00:48:31,617
Marilah, kita nak baca buku,
hasilkan seni dan belajar macam-macam.

717
00:48:34,745 --> 00:48:36,245
Betul tiada apa berlaku

718
00:48:36,246 --> 00:48:37,955
- sebelum Demo muncul?
- Ya.

719
00:48:37,956 --> 00:48:39,749
Cerita balik dari awal.

720
00:48:39,750 --> 00:48:41,668
- Dah cerita.
- Cerita lagi.

721
00:48:44,087 --> 00:48:46,548
Saya dan Mary di bulatan pusing.

722
00:48:47,132 --> 00:48:49,508
- Derek, janganlah!
- Pegang kuat-kuat!

723
00:48:49,509 --> 00:48:54,180
Derek buat perangai bangang macam biasa,
kemudian Henry panggil saya di sana.

724
00:48:54,181 --> 00:48:56,390
Dia kata dia nak lindungi saya.

725
00:48:56,391 --> 00:48:59,185
Saya tak jumpa dia lagi
sampai di padang itu.

726
00:48:59,186 --> 00:49:01,771
Saya dipanggil sebab ada kawan khayalan,

727
00:49:01,772 --> 00:49:05,817
kemudian mak berkelakuan pelik
dan bergaduh besar dengan ayah.

728
00:49:17,079 --> 00:49:18,079
Kenapa?

729
00:49:18,080 --> 00:49:20,665
Ada yang tak kena. Ia sepatutnya kuning.

730
00:49:20,666 --> 00:49:21,750
Berhenti!

731
00:49:39,184 --> 00:49:41,686
<i>Mak!</i>

732
00:49:41,687 --> 00:49:43,187
<i>Mak! Ayah!</i>

733
00:49:43,188 --> 00:49:46,233
<i>Tolong! Tolong lepaskan aku!</i>

734
00:49:47,901 --> 00:49:50,444
Mak!

735
00:49:50,445 --> 00:49:54,408
Tolong! Tolong, mak! Mak! Ayah!

736
00:49:57,786 --> 00:49:58,704
Ke belakang!

737
00:49:59,538 --> 00:50:00,956
Holly.

738
00:50:02,040 --> 00:50:03,417
Awak okey tak?

739
00:50:05,085 --> 00:50:06,503
Saya pun tak tahulah.

740
00:50:07,337 --> 00:50:08,337
Entah. Saya rasa...

741
00:50:08,338 --> 00:50:09,755
Takut?

742
00:50:09,756 --> 00:50:11,633
Memori terakhir dah dekat.

743
00:50:13,218 --> 00:50:16,345
Awak mungkin akan mula rasa sesuatu,

744
00:50:16,346 --> 00:50:18,348
perasaan awak pada malam itu.

745
00:50:19,599 --> 00:50:20,767
Saya pun alaminya.

746
00:50:22,853 --> 00:50:25,147
Tapi ia cuma macam gema.

747
00:50:25,814 --> 00:50:26,982
Itu petanda baik.

748
00:50:27,858 --> 00:50:29,818
Maknanya awak hampir boleh balik.

749
00:50:35,032 --> 00:50:36,658
Marilah. Ikut saya.

750
00:50:45,083 --> 00:50:47,711
Awak kata saya hampir boleh balik.

751
00:50:49,171 --> 00:50:51,298
Tapi awak akan ikut sekali, bukan?

752
00:50:52,340 --> 00:50:54,384
Tak. Saya nak tinggal di sini.

753
00:50:54,968 --> 00:50:57,178
Mestilah. Awak biar betul?

754
00:50:57,179 --> 00:50:58,138
Jom.

755
00:51:03,143 --> 00:51:04,518
- Hei!
- Apa kamu buat?

756
00:51:04,519 --> 00:51:05,936
Kabel tak jejak tanah.

757
00:51:05,937 --> 00:51:08,857
Kita kena buat eksperimen sains di atas.

758
00:51:15,572 --> 00:51:16,864
Okey.

759
00:51:16,865 --> 00:51:17,908
Perlahan-lahan.

760
00:51:20,243 --> 00:51:21,203
Okey.

761
00:51:23,413 --> 00:51:25,331
- Sedia? Sedia?
- Ya.

762
00:51:25,332 --> 00:51:26,708
Sedia!

763
00:51:48,355 --> 00:51:49,898
Okey, kita dah sedia.

764
00:51:55,695 --> 00:51:58,114
Kalau ada apa-apa jadi, keluar saja.

765
00:51:58,115 --> 00:51:59,865
Baik. Saya janji.

766
00:51:59,866 --> 00:52:02,952
Kalau keadaan jadi kacau,
kami akan naikkan voltan

767
00:52:02,953 --> 00:52:06,039
agar zarah rentung
dan putuskan dia daripada minda.

768
00:52:08,625 --> 00:52:10,293
- Mak?
- Ya?

769
00:52:10,877 --> 00:52:12,671
Terima kasih sebab percayakan saya.

770
00:52:15,048 --> 00:52:16,508
Bunuh bangsat itu.

771
00:52:17,884 --> 00:52:19,386
Baiklah. Kau boleh buat.

772
00:52:23,348 --> 00:52:24,807
Hidupkan, Frankenstein.

773
00:52:24,808 --> 00:52:26,685
Sebutannya "Fronkensteen"!

774
00:53:07,184 --> 00:53:10,144
Berkesan. Berkesan!

775
00:53:10,145 --> 00:53:11,730
Parasnya 50 peratus!

776
00:53:16,067 --> 00:53:17,027
Tolonglah.

777
00:53:42,093 --> 00:53:42,928
Bangang!

778
00:53:44,679 --> 00:53:46,764
Mana dia? Mana En. Whatsit?

779
00:53:46,765 --> 00:53:48,266
Rasanya aku Derek.

780
00:53:49,142 --> 00:53:51,645
- Derek?
- Dia ada bersama mereka.

781
00:53:52,562 --> 00:53:53,979
Budak-budak hilang itu.

782
00:53:53,980 --> 00:53:55,023
Holly pula?

783
00:53:55,607 --> 00:53:57,441
- Kau nampak Holly?
- Tak.

784
00:53:57,442 --> 00:54:01,654
Cepatlah jawab, bangang! Mana En. Whatsit?

785
00:54:01,655 --> 00:54:03,322
Cari Holly.

786
00:54:03,323 --> 00:54:06,951
Henry tengah cari dia.

787
00:54:06,952 --> 00:54:10,037
Holly takkan lari.
Dia tak macam itu. Kau tipu.

788
00:54:10,038 --> 00:54:12,873
Aku tak tipulah.
Ada raksasa perdayakan dia.

789
00:54:12,874 --> 00:54:16,460
Ia menyamar jadi perempuan
berbaju pelik dan berambut merah.

790
00:54:16,461 --> 00:54:17,378
Nama dia...

791
00:54:17,379 --> 00:54:18,295
Max.

792
00:54:18,296 --> 00:54:20,089
Sekejap. Kenapa dengan Max?

793
00:54:20,090 --> 00:54:21,216
Dia dengan Holly.

794
00:54:21,800 --> 00:54:24,594
Tapi Vecna tengah buru mereka.

795
00:54:35,855 --> 00:54:37,274
Saya tercegat saja.

796
00:54:38,775 --> 00:54:40,651
Kenapa saya tak tolong lawan?

797
00:54:40,652 --> 00:54:41,987
Itu Holly yang lama.

798
00:54:42,862 --> 00:54:43,738
Sekarang lain.

799
00:54:46,700 --> 00:54:49,953
Tidak! Mak! Mak, tolonglah!

800
00:54:50,787 --> 00:54:51,746
Jom.

801
00:55:13,685 --> 00:55:14,978
Apa itu?

802
00:55:16,354 --> 00:55:17,188
Jalan keluar.

803
00:55:17,772 --> 00:55:19,774
Tak nampak macam jalan keluar pun.

804
00:55:25,155 --> 00:55:27,073
Betulkah awak bukan raksasa?

805
00:55:27,907 --> 00:55:28,908
Betul.

806
00:55:37,667 --> 00:55:39,544
Aku dah pesan, Holly.

807
00:55:49,220 --> 00:55:50,972
Jangan masuk ke hutan.

808
00:55:55,643 --> 00:55:58,228
- Tak guna!
- Max, dia datang! Tidak!

809
00:55:58,229 --> 00:55:59,689
Holly, beri sini.

810
00:56:00,815 --> 00:56:02,359
Max, cepat!

811
00:56:29,677 --> 00:56:31,846
Akhirnya,

812
00:56:33,139 --> 00:56:35,642
si musang dah tertangkap.

813
00:56:36,643 --> 00:56:38,144
Berhenti!

814
00:56:51,825 --> 00:56:52,742
Max!

815
00:57:17,142 --> 00:57:18,393
Ia berkesan.

816
00:57:26,401 --> 00:57:27,277
Ahli sihir.

817
00:57:30,989 --> 00:57:32,907
Max! Awak tak apa-apa?

818
00:57:42,125 --> 00:57:43,750
- Max!
- Max!

819
00:57:43,751 --> 00:57:44,960
Kalau awak...

820
00:57:44,961 --> 00:57:48,005
...boleh dengar, tolong...

821
00:57:48,006 --> 00:57:50,175
- ...lari...
- ...sekarang!

822
00:57:51,468 --> 00:57:55,680
Lari!

823
00:58:18,119 --> 00:58:18,995
Keluar.

824
00:58:20,580 --> 00:58:21,748
Keluar!

825
00:58:22,957 --> 00:58:23,917
Keluar!

826
00:58:25,001 --> 00:58:26,460
Apa yang berlaku?

827
00:58:26,461 --> 00:58:27,504
Keluar!

828
00:58:28,588 --> 00:58:30,215
Keluar!

829
00:58:34,719 --> 00:58:36,512
- Will, dengar tak?
- Bangun!

830
00:58:36,513 --> 00:58:37,429
Mak ada.

831
00:58:37,430 --> 00:58:39,724
- Bangun, Will.
- Naikkan!

832
00:59:06,417 --> 00:59:07,960
Will, kembalilah.

833
00:59:07,961 --> 00:59:09,878
Kembalilah, Will. Will!

834
00:59:09,879 --> 00:59:11,880
- Tidak!
- Will, kembalilah!

835
00:59:11,881 --> 00:59:13,883
- Will!
- Kembalilah!

836
00:59:24,894 --> 00:59:26,771
Ada banyak benda cair ini lagi.

837
00:59:41,995 --> 00:59:42,996
Jonathan.

838
00:59:44,747 --> 00:59:45,790
Awak nampak tak?

839
00:59:47,917 --> 00:59:49,002
Apa?

840
00:59:49,877 --> 00:59:50,878
Lampu saya.

841
00:59:51,671 --> 00:59:52,672
Tengok.

842
01:00:09,981 --> 01:00:11,316
Ada sesuatu di sana.

843
01:00:44,432 --> 01:00:45,767
Sihir gelap.

844
01:00:49,020 --> 01:00:50,021
Ya Tuhan.

845
01:00:52,482 --> 01:00:54,441
<i>Dustin, Steve, dengar tak?</i>

846
01:00:54,442 --> 01:00:56,611
Kami jumpa penjana perisai. Dengar?

847
01:00:58,821 --> 01:01:00,781
Jonathan, ini Dustin. Dengar tak?

848
01:01:00,782 --> 01:01:04,993
Aku tak dengar. Kau dengar tak?
Kami dah jumpa penjana perisai itu.

849
01:01:04,994 --> 01:01:07,663
Dengar sini, okey? Jangan buat apa-apa.

850
01:01:07,664 --> 01:01:08,872
Jangan usik!

851
01:01:08,873 --> 01:01:10,208
<i>Jangan usik apa-apa!</i>

852
01:01:10,792 --> 01:01:11,668
Alamak!

853
01:01:16,964 --> 01:01:18,508
Mereka di luar lingkungan.

854
01:01:20,468 --> 01:01:23,262
Nampaknya, tak dapatlah mereka tengok.

855
01:01:37,235 --> 01:01:38,069
Jonathan!

856
01:01:39,404 --> 01:01:41,571
Kalau kau boleh dengar, aku silap!

857
01:01:41,572 --> 01:01:44,784
Itu sebenarnya bukan penjana perisai!

858
01:01:45,368 --> 01:01:48,120
Ia bukan sihir gelap, tapi benda lain!

859
01:01:48,121 --> 01:01:50,081
Jonathan! Nancy!

860
01:01:53,334 --> 01:01:55,001
Jonathan! Nancy!

861
01:01:55,002 --> 01:01:57,796
Kalau kamu hancurkannya, kamu akan mati!

862
01:01:57,797 --> 01:01:58,880
Kita akan mati!

863
01:01:58,881 --> 01:02:01,341
Holly akan mati! Semua orang akan mati!

864
01:02:01,342 --> 01:02:03,010
Boleh dengar tak?

865
01:02:05,263 --> 01:02:06,389
Awak yakinkah?

866
01:02:09,559 --> 01:02:10,518
Tak.

867
01:04:46,465 --> 01:04:50,887
Terjemahan sari kata oleh M Arrazi Azmi

